  "markup": "\u003Cp class=\u0022p1\u0022\u003EExplores the knee joint and common pathologies found in clinical practice, including tendinitis, bursitis, sprains, and more.\u0026nbsp; Evaluates the available data on successful treatments with Super Pulsed Laser. \u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C!--\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg height=\u0022505\u0022 width=\u0022590\u0022 src=\u0022~/media/D6E155C624494C559F7068F7FB4C044E.ashx\u0022 alt=\u0022April 2012 LTU Webinar\u0022 /\u003E\u003C/p\u003E--\u003E"
